reviews.title: Thank you cm-moru for an excellent app!
reviews.comment: This app is great my 2yr old granddaughter Mia loves it, when she is on my tablet all she want is songs and goes straight to you tube to her subscribed channels. Now she has everything she wants and more in one great app, I recommend also installing kids movies, and baby videos by the same developer. I particularly appreciate The Classical Musical by this developer for when Mia goes home and I can use my tablet myself. Five stars but wanted to give 4.5 because there aren\'t any Mickey Mouse Clubhouse.
